This is a command line version of famous game 2048.

To compile on linux:
--------------------

gcc -o 2048 2048.c -lncurses

It will not compile on Windows because of ncurses library.
I am working on making it compile on windows.

TO Run:
-------

Run 2048 program and start playing.

Press ctrl-C any time to exit.

Press key 'n' to start a new Game

Enjoy!
